OL,3,CWhy recession is now 'the base case'
OL,5,FAs the febrile financial markets
OL,6,Fawaken again in Tokyo, it's clear that
OL,7,Fthe next 48 hours will be critical in
OL,8,Fdeciding whether the US can avoid a
OL,9,Frecession and the world a painful
OL,10,Fgrowth deceleration.
OL,12,FBecause Trump and his record-breaking
OL,13,Ftariffs - and China's tit-for-tat
OL,14,Fretaliation - have forced a triple
OL,15,Fwhammy on the US.
OL,17,FHit number one is the tariffs
OL,18,Fthemselves, which put up the costs of
OL,19,Fgoods and foods, and crush the income
OL,20,Fof consumers and businesses.
