OL,5,FI have reported at the frontline of
OL,6,Fquite a few financial and economic
OL,7,Fcrises, and this one has elements of
OL,8,Fthe self-inflicted harm in 2008 when
OL,9,FUS regulators refused to put Lehman
OL,10,FBros on life support and the
OL,11,Fdemocratically chosen harm to the UK's
OL,12,Fgrowth prospects in 2016 when British
OL,13,Fpeople voted to leave the EU.
